      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's gotten really loud in my head lately. like i can feel everyone's frustration, the millions of people who dont get a say in anything. i think i'm finally tuned in to them. the silent majority is speaking through me. can you help me figure out what they are trying to say about the new energy policy? what is their collective will?",
